<div class="music-list" style="margin-top:20px;"><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/minima-moralia.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/minimamoralia.jpg" alt="Minima Moralia / Chihei Hatakeyama" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/minima-moralia.php">Minima Moralia<br />Chihei Hatakeyama</a></h4><p>ゆったりとした時間が流れていく音楽。心が落ち着けるだけではなく、つい耳を澄ましてしまうようなポップさも持つ素晴らしい作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000E8NQLI?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000E8NQLI" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Minima Moralia-Chihei Hatakeyama']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fminima-moralia%252Fid118924960%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Minima Moralia-Chihei Hatakeyama']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/apikalblend.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/apikalblend.jpg" alt="Apikal.Blend / Sogar" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/apikalblend.php">Apikal.Blend<br />Sogar</a></h4><p>IDMサウンドですが、優しい雰囲気を持った作品です。音の質感が心地よくずっと聴いていたくなるような音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0010WW320?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0010WW320" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Apikal.Blend-Sogar']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fapikal-blend%252Fid34279374%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Apikal.Blend-Sogar']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/stil.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/stil.jpg" alt="Stil. / Taylor Deupree" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/stil.php">Stil.<br />Taylor Deupree</a></h4><p>朝、起床したときなどにずっと流したままにしておきたくなるような脱力感を誘う音楽。時間を贅沢に使っているような気分になれます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0011F087I?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0011F087I" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Stil.-Taylor Deupree']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fstil%252Fid16731432%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Stil.-Taylor Deupree']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/atom-document.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/atomdocument.jpg" alt="Atom / Document / Robert Henke" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/atom-document.php">Atom / Document<br />Robert Henke</a></h4><p>生活音が鳴ってるような錯覚を起こしてしまうような音楽。どこかで聴いたことがあるような音で、気分が休まるような音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B001J32H58?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B001J32H58" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Atom / Document-Robert Henke']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fatom-document%252Fid301565831%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Atom / Document-Robert Henke']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/periphery.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/periphery.jpg" alt="Periphery / Christopher Bissonnette" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/periphery.php">Periphery<br />Christopher Bissonnette</a></h4><p>壮大な世界観を感じることができる作品。とても美しい音がたくさん聴こえてくるので心が洗われるような気がしてきます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000B3MIQ0?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000B3MIQ0" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Periphery-Christopher Bissonnette']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fperiphery%252Fid81355775%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Periphery-Christopher Bissonnette']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/harmony-in-ultraviolet.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/harmonyinultraviolet.jpg" alt="Harmony In Ultraviolet / Tim Hecker" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/harmony-in-ultraviolet.php">Harmony In Ultraviolet<br />Tim Hecker</a></h4><p>シリアスで緊張感を感じながら聴くことができる作品です。耳に痛いような音ではなく、聴いていて想像力をかき立てられる音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000INAWRK?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000INAWRK" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Harmony In Ultraviolet-Tim Hecker']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fharmony-in-ultraviolet%252Fid189047071%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Harmony In Ultraviolet-Tim Hecker']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/dropsonde.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/dropsonde.jpg" alt="Dropsonde / Biosphere" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/dropsonde.php">Dropsonde<br />Biosphere</a></h4><p>映画の1シーンのような壮大で美しい音楽。静かさの中に美しさを感じることができるアンビエントミュージックの傑作です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000CNF50U?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000CNF50U" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Dropsonde-Biosphere']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fdropsonde%252Fid122993492%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Dropsonde-Biosphere']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/maybe-they-will-sing-for-us-tomorrow.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/maybe.jpg" alt="Maybe They Will Sing for Us Tomorrow / Hammock" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/maybe-they-will-sing-for-us-tomorrow.php">Maybe They Will Sing for Us Tomorrow<br />Hammock</a></h4><p>氷のような透き通った音楽で、まるで雪国を訪れているような気分にさせてくれます。心地よい音色も魅力のひとつです。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0016MJ2IW?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0016MJ2IW" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Maybe They Will Sing for Us Tomorrow-Hammock']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fmaybe-they-will-sing-for-us%252Fid278529731%253Fi%253D278529905%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%25" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Maybe They Will Sing for Us Tomorrow-Hammock']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/evolutions.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/evolutions.jpg" alt="Evolutions / Tobias Hellkvist" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/evolutions.php">Evolutions<br />Tobias Hellkvist</a></h4><p>身近な雰囲気を持つ音楽。小さな部屋で鳴り響いているかのような音の「近さ」が最大の魅力の1枚です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003ENHDHS?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003ENHDHS" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Evolutions-Tobias Hellkvist']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fsore%252Fid368335473%253Fi%253D368335508%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTISTNAME: Tobias" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Evolutions-Tobias Hellkvist']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

